    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1187673>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Ascidia interrupta (st. AR 415): A, neural gland duct stained with hemalum; B, dorsal tubercle area; C, detail of the neural ductapertures." ;
